column2: SELECT   s.z,s.velDisp,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, zS.spiral, zS.elliptical, zS.uncertain, zS.p_mg FROM SpecObj AS s  JOIN galSpecIndx AS gi ON s.specObjID = gi.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra AS ge ON s.specObjID = ge.specObjID  JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sph ON s.specObjID = sph.specObjID  JOIN zooSpec AS zS ON s.specObjID = zS.specObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND  s.survey = &&&  AND  s.class = &&&  AND  s.snMedian_r > #  AND  s.zWARNING = #  AND  zS.uncertain = #
